{"tid":1564464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我信有白警  一定有  跪求大家入黎比d鼓勵  唔好鬧","createTime":"2019-09-12T18:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T04:02:27.000Z","uid":166129,"like":37,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"92dea838c9cc64b07efdac0493e229ec488d8b02","tid":1564464,"uid":166129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T18:56:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">警察先生  <br />\n我相信你好明白以家香港發生緊咩事<br />\n亦清楚知道再咁落去 你在乎既人 你既下一代<br />\n將會活係一個點既社會<br />\n<br />\n你都係香港人  請你諗返起  <br />\n由細到大 係呢度經歷既一切 人 事 物<br />\n係呢度長大  <br />\n係呢度遇到你既另一半  <br />\n係呢度建立你既家庭<br />\n<br />\n我充心相信  <br />\n你係有方法幫到呢個地方<br />\n<br />\n懇請你 <br />\n為你自己 為你身邊人  為下一代 為香港<br />\n鼓起勇氣</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做一次 英雄</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">即使你可能會因此而付出某d代價<br />\n<br />\n但我肯定<br />\n<br />\n香港 同所有香港人 會證明比你睇  我地係值得既。</span>"},{"pid":"5b6b67d983c3bdefa52984d6b6fa45cd176be4ac","tid":1564464,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T18:56:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"7562b273010fbe321e85b384f2d941d6983615cc","tid":1564464,"uid":49979,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"reply